spec_data.Name: basesystem
spec_data.Description:
Basesystem defines the components of a basic Fedora system
(for example, the package installation order to use during bootstrapping).
Basesystem should be in every installation of a system, and it
should never be removed.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Tue 01 Aug 2017 04:09:45 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: The skeleton package which defines a simple Fedora system
